snippet.textDisplay: Thank you John Krasinski for bringing some light into our currently darkened world. I tried so hard to not laugh the first few minutes, but when those office clips started playing, I just couldn't anymore. I am so glad you got into acting. I loved the entire series and I (just like every other female fan) always thought you were cute, so that helped. Lmao but the whole cast was great. Steve is hilarious also. I really hope you guys do that reunion after all this is over. It would be very uplifting for the fans and provide some comic relief. I subscribed here. Please keep making these videos and encouraging people to send in good news. We need it so badly right now. 💙 Huge fan. Chrissy
